            <title>[LU-5427] Lustre cannot be compiled with MPSS 3.3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5427</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are few changes in names happens in recent version of MPSS 3.3:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The name of main archive is not depends from OS name any more and named as &lt;tt&gt;mpss-&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;-linux.tar&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The name of MPSS OFED devel package was changed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The name of MPSS OFED directory with headers was changed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
